abstract: Miami-Dade police officer fatally shoots man, identified as Junior Prosper, along Miami's Interstate 95 after Prosper crashes taxi, runs up an entrance ramp and bites one of officer's fingers during confrontation.
lead_paragraph: A police officer shot and killed a man who bit one of the officer’s fingers during an encounter Monday morning along Interstate 95 in Miami, the Miami-Dade police said.

headline.main: Florida: Officer Killed Man Who Bit Him, Police Say
